While searching the Pharmacy aisle, you come across another scavenger with danger on his mind.
As you enter, you spot another person who stands menacingly, glaring at you.
Looking for your favorite brand of canned peaches, you hear footsteps and spot another person, who doesn't look like the sharing type.
Entering the store, you spot another survivor, who's for some reason checking out? Being caught in the act, embarassment taints his expression, he tries to fight you.